  schema:name "Accelerating Expansion" ;
  schema:description "The accelerating expansion is the observed fact that the [expansion of the universe](./cosmic-expansion.md) is speeding up rather than slowing down. It was discovered in 1998 and is caused by [dark energy](../../structure/terms/dark-energy.md)." ;
